  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Production Admin",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />We are seeking a detail-oriented and reliable Production Admin to provide key support to the production line. The primary responsibility is to accurately prepare and manage labels, packaging, and other materials based on the daily production schedule to ensure smooth operations.</p><p><strong>主要职责：</strong><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ol><li><p><strong>物料与标签管理：</strong> 根据生产计划，准时、准确地打印、分发产品标签及文件。管理包装耗材的库存、领取与补充。<br /><strong>Material & Label Management:</strong> Print and distribute product labels and documents accurately and on time according to the production schedule. Manage the inventory, issuance, and replenishment of packaging consumables.</p></li><li><p><strong>生产支持：</strong> 维护工作区域整洁，处理相关生产文件与基础数据，操作和维护标签打印设备。<br /><strong>Production Support:</strong> Maintain a tidy work area, handle relevant production documents and basic data entry, operate and perform basic maintenance on label printing equipment.</p></li><li><p><strong>准确性与合规：</strong> 确保所有标签与物料符合要求，支持质量追溯与记录。<br /><strong>Accuracy & Compliance:</strong> Ensure all labels and materials meet specifications and support quality traceability and documentation.</p></li></ol><p><strong>任职要求：</strong><br /><strong>Qualifications & Skills:</strong></p><ul><li><p>高中或以上学历。<br />O level or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>熟悉电脑及Office软件（尤其是Excel）。有标签打印机操作经验者优先。<br />Proficient with computers and Microsoft Office (especially Excel). Experience with barcode label printers is a plus.</p></li><li><p>工作细心，有责任心，能适应重复性任务。具备良好的条理性和团队合作精神。<br />Detail-oriented, responsible, and able to handle repetitive tasks accurately. Good organizational and teamwork skills.</p></li></ul>",
